snippet.title: 「Gregorius」 Piano Epic Performance (Full Ver) / Blue archive Total Assualt OST "Symphony(Theme 158)"
snippet.description:
Blue Archive - "Symphony(Theme 158)" Total Assualt Boss 「Gregorius」 OST Piano Performance (Full Ver.)


Today's performance is the theme of the Blue archive Total Assualt boss "Gregorius".

As the most recent Total Assualt Boss on the Japanese server,
He is also the main character of the OST "Symphony(Theme 158)" that many people have been waiting for.

In order to play the original song with one hand, some adaptations are needed,
I decided that it would be difficult to preserve all the crazy splendor and profound taste of the original song.
Arranged & performed as a briquette song.

This "Gregorius" has music for each pattern even within Total Assualt, etc.
There are a lot of different aspects, and I also considered those aspects a lot.

In particular, the intro section of "Maestro" and "Gregorius" pattern music
It started off pretty fresh.

When making a video, I tend to try a lot to upload without mistakes.
But, this time. There are quite a few mistakes in this video.
I ask for your understanding lol

Thank you for listening
